# Casper Shops

## Description
Casper Shops is a decentralized commerce solution enabling independent buyers & sellers to contribute & be rewarded for the exchange of goods & services. 
The system provides mechanisms to automate online e-commerce sales tracking. 
Casper storefronts will provide the ability to mint NFTs & register physical goods such as merchandise for sale. The NFTs can represent real goods, services & digital products.

## Status

**Grant Accepted** / In progress / Completed

